;; Yandex 360 (business mail) DNS records for skazkamuseum.ru
;; Import in Cloudflare: DNS -> Records -> Import and Export -> Import DNS records
;;
;; !! BEFORE importing: DELETE the existing SPF record in Cloudflare
;;    (TXT @ "v=spf1 include:spf.unisender.ru ~all") — a domain may have ONE SPF
;;    record only. The record below REPLACES it and authorizes BOTH senders:
;;    Unisender (ticket/site emails) and Yandex (mailboxes like spb@/noreply@).
;;
;; All records must stay "DNS only" (grey cloud), never proxied.
$ORIGIN skazkamuseum.ru.
$TTL 1800

;; SPF — merged: Unisender + Yandex in one record
@	1800	IN	TXT	"v=spf1 include:spf.unisender.ru include:_spf.yandex.net ~all"

;; Mail delivery INTO the Yandex mailboxes (standard Yandex 360 MX)
@	1800	IN	MX	10 mx.yandex.net.

;; Yandex will also ask for (add when its wizard shows the values):
;;  - domain ownership TXT:   @  TXT  "yandex-verification=XXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX"
;;  - DKIM key:               mail._domainkey  TXT  "v=DKIM1; k=rsa; p=MIGf..."
;; Paste those to Claude and they'll be added here.
